bwean authors to break into the genre. His works have also put Zimbabwean literature on the global fantasy map.", "Simon Makoni has greatly contributed to Zimbabwe's literary scene. His triumph as a globally recognized fantasy author has fostered a new generation of Zimbabwean authors to break into the genre. His works have also put Zimbabwean literature on the global fantasy map.")]}
